[
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "chapter"
    },
    "innerText": "12. Soḷasanipāto"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "subhead"
    },
    "innerText": "1. Puṇṇātherīgāthāvaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      "Soḷasanipāte ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "udahārī ahaṃ sīte"
      },
      "tiādikā puṇṇāya theriyā gāthā. Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikārā tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayaṃ kusalaṃ upacinantī vipassissa bhagavato kāle kulagehe nibbattitvā viññutaṃ patvā hetusampannatāya sañjātasaṃvegā bhikkhunīnaṃ santikaṃ gantvā dhammaṃ sutvā laddhappasādā pabbajitvā parisuddhasīlā tīṇi piṭakāni uggahetvā bahussutā dhammadharā dhammakathikā ca ahosi. Yathā ca vipassissa bhagavato sāsane, evaṃ sikhissa vessabhussa kakusandhassa koṇāgamanassa kassapassa ",
      " ca bhagavato sāsane pabbajitvā sīlasampannā bahussutā dhammadharā dhammakathikā ca ahosi. Mānadhātukattā pana kilese samucchindituṃ nāsakkhi. Mānopanissayavasena kammassa katattā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde anāthapiṇḍikassa seṭṭhino gharadāsiyā kucchimhi nibbatti, ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "puṇṇā"
      },
      "tissā nāmaṃ ahosi. Sā ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "sīhanādasuttantadesanāya"
      },
      " (ma. ni. 1.146 ādayo) sotāpannā hutvā pacchā udakasuddhikaṃ brāhmaṇaṃ dametvā seṭṭhinā sambhāvitā hutvā tena bhujissabhāvaṃ pāpitā taṃ pabbajjaṃ anujānāpetvā pabbajitvā vipassanāya kammaṃ karontī na cirasseva saha paṭisambhidāhi arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. Tena vuttaṃ ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "apadāne"
      },
      " (apa. therī 2.4.184-203) –"
    ],
    "innerText": "Soḷasanipāte udahārī ahaṃ sītetiādikā puṇṇāya theriyā gāthā. Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikārā tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayaṃ kusalaṃ upacinantī vipassissa bhagavato kāle kulagehe nibbattitvā viññutaṃ patvā hetusampannatāya sañjātasaṃvegā bhikkhunīnaṃ santikaṃ gantvā dhammaṃ sutvā laddhappasādā pabbajitvā parisuddhasīlā tīṇi piṭakāni uggahetvā bahussutā dhammadharā dhammakathikā ca ahosi. Yathā ca vipassissa bhagavato sāsane, evaṃ sikhissa vessabhussa kakusandhassa koṇāgamanassa kassapassa ca bhagavato sāsane pabbajitvā sīlasampannā bahussutā dhammadharā dhammakathikā ca ahosi. Mānadhātukattā pana kilese samucchindituṃ nāsakkhi. Mānopanissayavasena kammassa katattā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde anāthapiṇḍikassa seṭṭhino gharadāsiyā kucchimhi nibbatti, puṇṇātissā nāmaṃ ahosi. Sā sīhanādasuttantadesanāya (ma. ni. 1.146 ādayo) sotāpannā hutvā pacchā udakasuddhikaṃ brāhmaṇaṃ dametvā seṭṭhinā sambhāvitā hutvā tena bhujissabhāvaṃ pāpitā taṃ pabbajjaṃ anujānāpetvā pabbajitvā vipassanāya kammaṃ karontī na cirasseva saha paṭisambhidāhi arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. Tena vuttaṃ apadāne (apa. therī 2.4.184-203) –"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gatha1"
    },
    "innerText": "‘‘Vipassino bhagavato, sikhino vessabhussa ca;"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gathalast"
    },
    "innerText": "Kakusandhassa munino, koṇāgamanatādino."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gatha1"
    },
    "innerText": "‘‘Kassapassa ca buddhassa, pabbajitvāna sāsane;"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gathalast"
    },
    "innerText": "Bhikkhunī sīlasampannā, nipakā saṃvutindriyā."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gatha1"
    },
    "innerText": "‘‘Bahussutā dhammadharā, dhammatthapaṭipucchikā;"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gathalast"
    },
    "innerText": "Uggahetā ca dhammānaṃ, sotā payirupāsitā."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gatha1"
    },
    "children": [
      "‘‘Desentī ",
      " janamajjhehaṃ, ahosiṃ jinasāsane;"
    ],
    "innerText": "‘‘Desentī janamajjhehaṃ, ahosiṃ jinasāsane;"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gathalast"
    },
    "innerText": "Bāhusaccena tenāhaṃ, pesalā abhimaññisaṃ."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gatha1"
    },
    "children": [
      "‘‘Pacchime ",
      " ca bhave dāni, sāvatthiyaṃ puruttame;"
    ],
    "innerText": "‘‘Pacchime ca bhave dāni, sāvatthiyaṃ puruttame;"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gathalast"
    },
    "innerText": "Anāthapiṇḍino gehe, jātāhaṃ kumbhadāsiyā."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gatha1"
    },
    "innerText": "‘‘Gatā udakahāriyaṃ, sotthiyaṃ dijamaddasaṃ;"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gathalast"
    },
    "innerText": "Sītaṭṭaṃ toyamajjhamhi, taṃ disvā idamabraviṃ."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gatha1"
    },
    "innerText": "‘‘Udahārī ahaṃ sīte, sadā udakamotariṃ;"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gathalast"
    },
    "innerText": "Ayyānaṃ daṇḍabhayabhītā, vācādosabhayaṭṭitā."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gatha1"
    },
    "innerText": "‘‘Kassa brāhmaṇa tvaṃ bhīto, sadā udakamotari;"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gathalast"
    },
    "innerText": "Vedhamānehi gattehi, sītaṃ vedayase bhusaṃ."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gatha1"
    },
    "innerText": "‘‘Jānantī vata maṃ bhoti, puṇṇike paripucchasi;"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gathalast"
    },
    "children": [
      "Karontaṃ ",
      " kusalaṃ kammaṃ, rundhantaṃ katapāpakaṃ."
    ],
    "innerText": "Karontaṃ kusalaṃ kammaṃ, rundhantaṃ katapāpakaṃ."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gatha1"
    },
    "innerText": "‘‘Yo ca vuḍḍho daharo vā, pāpakammaṃ pakubbati;"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gathalast"
    },
    "innerText": "Dakābhisecanā sopi, pāpakammā pamuccati."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gatha1"
    },
    "innerText": "‘‘Uttarantassa akkhāsiṃ, dhammatthasaṃhitaṃ padaṃ;"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gathalast"
    },
    "innerText": "Tañca sutvā sa saṃviggo, pabbajitvārahā ahu."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gatha1"
    },
    "innerText": "‘‘Pūrentī ūnakasataṃ, jātā dāsikule yato;"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gathalast"
    },
    "innerText": "Tato puṇṇāti nāmaṃ me, bhujissaṃ maṃ akaṃsu te."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gatha1"
    },
    "innerText": "‘‘Seṭṭhiṃ tatonujānetvā, pabbajiṃ anagāriyaṃ;"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gathalast"
    },
    "innerText": "Na cireneva kālena, arahattamapāpuṇiṃ."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gatha1"
    },
    "children": [
      "‘‘Iddhīsu ",
      " ca vasī homi, dibbāya sotadhātuyā;"
    ],
    "innerText": "‘‘Iddhīsu ca vasī homi, dibbāya sotadhātuyā;"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gathalast"
    },
    "innerText": "Cetopariyañāṇassa, vasī homi mahāmune."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gatha1"
    },
    "innerText": "‘‘Pubbenivāsaṃ jānāmi, dibbacakkhu visodhitaṃ;"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gathalast"
    },
    "innerText": "Sabbāsavaparikkhīṇā, natthi dāni punabbhavo."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gatha1"
    },
    "innerText": "‘‘Atthadhammaniruttīsu, paṭibhāne tatheva ca;"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gathalast"
    },
    "innerText": "Ñāṇaṃ me vimalaṃ suddhaṃ, buddhaseṭṭhassa vāhasā."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gatha1"
    },
    "children": [
      "‘‘Bhāvanāya ",
      " mahāpaññā, suteneva sutāvinī;"
    ],
    "innerText": "‘‘Bhāvanāya mahāpaññā, suteneva sutāvinī;"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gathalast"
    },
    "innerText": "Mānena nīcakulajā, na hi kammaṃ vinassati."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gatha1"
    },
    "innerText": "‘‘Kilesā jhāpitā mayhaṃ…pe… kataṃ buddhassa sāsana’’nti."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "innerText": "Arahattaṃ pana patvā attano paṭipattiṃ paccavekkhitvā udānavasena –"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "hangnum"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "236"
      },
      "."
    ],
    "innerText": "236."
  },
