    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Puññampi mā vaheyyu"
      },
      "nti imā aciravatiādayo nadiyo yathā tayā pubbe kataṃ pāpaṃ tattha udakābhisecanena sace vahuṃ nīhareyyuṃ, tathā tayā kataṃ puññampi imā nadiyo vaheyyuṃ pavāheyyuṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Tena tvaṃ"
      },
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "paribāhiro"
      },
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "assa"
      },
      " tathā sati tena puññakammena tvaṃ paribāhiro virahitova bhaveyyāti na cetaṃ yuttanti adhippāyo. Yathā vā udakena udakorohakassa puññapavāhanaṃ na hoti, evaṃ pāpapavāhanampi na hoti eva. Kasmā? Nhānassa pāpahetūnaṃ appaṭipakkhabhāvato. Yo yaṃ vināseti, so tassa paṭipakkho. Yathā āloko andhakārassa, vijjā ca avijjāya, na evaṃ nhānaṃ pāpassa. Tasmā niṭṭhamettha gantabbaṃ ‘‘na udakābhisecanā pāpato parimuttī’’ti. Tenāha bhagavā –"
    ],
    "innerText": "Puññampi mā vaheyyunti imā aciravatiādayo nadiyo yathā tayā pubbe kataṃ pāpaṃ tattha udakābhisecanena sace vahuṃ nīhareyyuṃ, tathā tayā kataṃ puññampi imā nadiyo vaheyyuṃ pavāheyyuṃ. Tena tvaṃparibāhiroassa tathā sati tena puññakammena tvaṃ paribāhiro virahitova bhaveyyāti na cetaṃ yuttanti adhippāyo. Yathā vā udakena udakorohakassa puññapavāhanaṃ na hoti, evaṃ pāpapavāhanampi na hoti eva. Kasmā? Nhānassa pāpahetūnaṃ appaṭipakkhabhāvato. Yo yaṃ vināseti, so tassa paṭipakkho. Yathā āloko andhakārassa, vijjā ca avijjāya, na evaṃ nhānaṃ pāpassa. Tasmā niṭṭhamettha gantabbaṃ ‘‘na udakābhisecanā pāpato parimuttī’’ti. Tenāha bhagavā –"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gatha1"
    },
    "innerText": "‘‘Na udakena sucī hoti, bahvettha nhāyatī jano;"
